.DS_Store
*.log

# Rust build artifacts
/target
Cargo.lock.bak

# Binary (release builds)
/claim
dist/

# Local, per-project claim caches (D3). Tracked files under claims/
# are genesis.amc, changes/<hash>.amc, and config.toml. Everything
# else is derived and must stay untracked.
claims/view.sqlite
claims/view.sqlite-journal
claims/view.sqlite-wal
claims/view.sqlite-shm
claims/view.heads
claims/snapshot.amc
claims/.lock
claims/_view.snapshot.nq
claims/_view.heads.json
# v3 gamma index: a disposable redb cache rebuilt from the log union.
claims/_view.oxigraph/
claims/_view.gamma.redb
claims/_view.gamma.redb-lock
